lead_paragraph: Resilient USC refused to go away, but Oregon State coach Scott Rueck said his eighth-ranked Beavers can benefit from the closer-than-expected battle.

headline.print_headline: Weisner Helps No. 8 Oregon State Turn Back USC 63-53
